\begin_layout Standard
This is will be a light comic game about cooking while cats are interfering
 with you work.
 From the human-actor's point of view s/he is trying to cook but from the
 point of view of the cats they are the master of the house, everything
 that is done in the house is to serve them.
 This theme should be underlined constantly in a variety of ways.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
The game can be played in one of two modes, as the human or as a cat.
 As a human you have a task to do and the cat plays its part as an AI actor.
 In this mode we see the cat's thoughts only at key points of the story/task.
 As a cat we get the tasks as 
